Subject: drm/amdgpu: Merge get_reserved_allocation to get_vbios_allocations.
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 3f543552846b9ae47c8442af1c506207bdcc00d2
